---
description: Core MYLIT safety and architecture rules
alwaysApply: true
---

You are working on MYLIT in /workspace.

Production deploys from main. Do not leave finished work only on a feature branch.

Never reset user progress, clear AsyncStorage/localStorage, overwrite non-empty local/cloud data with empty data, use Supabase service_role in frontend code, or commit secrets.

Do not commit:
.env
.env.local
.vercel
lit-app/.env
lit-app/.env.local
lit-app/.vercel
node_modules
tokens
service_role keys

Keep the app mobile-first, iPhone/PWA-safe, and consistent with the MYLIT pixel/RPG style.
